{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": true, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 148733, "create_time": 1653487839, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "公选课有什么影响嘛，反正都是系内卷，不会真的有人选不同的思政课是为了听更好的老师讲课叭，区别不是仅仅在于给分和任务量等", "timestamp": 1653487839}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 148739, "create_time": 1653487971, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "啊？软院同学表示一直专业课全是三志愿啊", "timestamp": 1653487971}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 148744, "create_time": 1653488107, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "xs软院课专业课序号都是0  么得选  全是三志愿", "timestamp": 1653488107}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 148755, "create_time": 1653488264, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "不是“必修>限选>任选”吗？没看懂dz在说什么，你是不是搞错了什么？\n只在必修里抢课不就只是和同专业的人抢吗？这样都会抢不到专业课吗？\n\n顺便我可以告诉你至少物理系也有必修课要上。而且我们很多必修课只有一个老师开，甚至嫌老师讲得烂换人的权利都没有/", "timestamp": 1653488264}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 148773, "create_time": 1653488535, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Dave: 同专业选课内卷，志愿很多1,2\n", "timestamp": 1653488535}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 148774, "create_time": 1653488572, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "软院有什么课开了两节吗？", "timestamp": 1653488572}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 148777, "create_time": 1653488717, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "dz是软院分流到贵系的，上学期就有这个问题，本来上学期软院这边一切正常，然后贵系就把限选全改成必修了，结果软院和贵系协调的结果是软院也全变成必修了。\ndz无语的是这学期继承了上学期的这一操作。", "timestamp": 1653488717}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 148781, "create_time": 1653488770, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Eve: 我对这学期软院的课的老师数量不太了解，感谢指正！\n", "timestamp": 1653488770}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 148786, "create_time": 1653488821, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 这难道不重要吗？[无奈的苦笑]", "timestamp": 1653488821}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 148802, "create_time": 1653489226, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "（不是说软和贵）有的降转同学遇到的比这更离谱，年年课程限xxxx级xx系学生选，只能等正选吃残羹剩饭。自己系的还能和老师说一说通融一下，有时候选其他系的课直接寄，你清教务的奇怪操作也见怪不怪了。", "timestamp": 1653489226}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 148818, "create_time": 1653489581, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "确实，离谱，都怪贵系", "timestamp": 1653489581}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 148822, "create_time": 1653489627, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "dz说的应该是大一大类的专业课", "timestamp": 1653489627}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 148825, "create_time": 1653489694, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "但事实上，软院大二之后的专业课就没这个问题了，因为没得选()", "timestamp": 1653489694}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 148842, "create_time": 1653490044, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Grace: 那还好\n", "timestamp": 1653490044}], "create_time": 1653487734, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1653490044, "likenum": 7, "n_attentions": 7, "n_comments": 14, "pid": 50213, "poll": null, "reply": 14, "text": "#选课相关\n#略引战\n我不明白为什么软院和贵系要把自己的专业课设成必修，以前一直是限选啊！\n对于像dz这样的普通同学来说，设成必修这件事相当不利。首先，这会造成本专业的同学分配志愿十分的困难，很多专业课只能改用必修3志愿来选，不过还好，反正也是只有本专业的同学来选。我觉得最离谱的是，这种操作使得软院/贵系的同学在选一部分专业课时占用了1、2志愿，导致像马原等公共思政课只能用2、3志愿。而一些必修较少专业或专业课不需要抢的专业的同学就可以用手中的1志愿去砸公共课，导致了软院/贵系的同学在选课中处于极大的劣势！（无意引战）\n不知道其他院系有没有这种情况，dz真心希望学校教务可以把专业课恢复成限选，以实现选课上的院系平等。", "timestamp": 1653487734}}